We need a place to store the scans permanently. For IoT, DynamoDB is perfect because it's fast and scales automatically.
Go to the DynamoDB Console > Tables > Create table.
Table name: StudentAttendance.
Partition key: student_id (String).
Sort key: timestamp (Number).
Why a Sort Key? This allows one student to have multiple entries (one for every day they scan).
Keep everything else as Default and click Create table.
